  Locus:
    Page: 424
    Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Service
---
Life is best spent in alleviating pain, assuaging distress, and promoting
peace and joy. The service of man is more valuable than what you call
“service to God.” God has no need of your service. Please man, you please
God.
